m\": 797, \"to\": 817}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was slated to lock horns with Sarah Hildebrandt of the US on 7 August in the 50kg weights category, but lost her bid aftershe was found to be 100g overweighton the morning of the match.\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 1009, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 854, \"end\": 871, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Hildebrandt\", \"score\": 0.9999999987971933, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sarah Hildebrandt\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Hildebrandt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Hildebrandt\"}, {\"begin\": 879, \"end\": 881, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.561303711219284, \"rank\": 0.7752938643345377, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"horns\", \"from\": 843, \"to\": 848}, {\"ngram\": \"7 August\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 893}, {\"ngram\": \"the 50kg weights category\", \"from\": 897, \"to\": 922}, {\"ngram\": \"her bid aftershe\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 949}, {\"ngram\": \"100g overweighton\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 983}, {\"ngram\": \"the match\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1008}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her appeal at CAS was twice delayed before India's hopes of a seventh Paris medal were dashed on Wednesday, as the ad-hoc division of the CAS rejected her appeal.\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1173, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1025, \"end\": 1028, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Court_of_Arbitration_for_Sport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0392091113024236e-25, \"text\": \"CAS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Court_of_Arbitration_for_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Court_of_Arbitration_for_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 1054, \"end\": 1059, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9