ns\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1747}, {\"ngram\": \"undue \\\"physiological and psychological stresses\", \"from\": 1753, \"to\": 1800}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 1813}, {\"ngram\": \"the association\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 1830}, {\"ngram\": \"a stark reminder\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 1871}, {\"ngram\": \"the need\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 1883}, {\"ngram\": \"more equitable and reasonable standards\", \"from\": 1888, \"to\": 1927}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes' well-being\", \"from\": 1944, \"to\": 1964}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Indian sporting body said it was providing ongoing support to Phogat and exploring further legal options, though it was unclear what those might be.\", \"from\": 1968, \"to\": 2120, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1972, \"end\": 1978, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"score\": 0.9996030726203521, \"rank\": 0.0003970849583531144, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\"}, {\"begin\": 2034, \"end\": 2040, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ongoing support\", \"from\": 2015, \"to\": 2030}, {\"ngram\": \"further legal options\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2076}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A day after her disqualification last week, Phogat announced that she was retiring from the sport.\", \"from\": 2122, \"to\": 2220, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2166, \"end\": 2172, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her disqualification\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2154}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 2210, \"to\": 2219}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a post written in Hindi, she said: \\\"My courage is broken, I do not have any more strength now.\", \"from\": 2221, \"to\": 2318, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2242, \"end\": 2247, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hindi\", \"score\": 0.9995328872337019, \"rank\": 0.0004673093380026541, \"text\": \"Hindi\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hindi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hindi\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a post\", \"from\": 2224, \"to\": 2230}, {\"ngram\": \"My courage\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2270}, {\"ngram\": \"any more strength\", \"from\": 2296, \"to\": 2313}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Goodbye Wrestling, 2001-2024.\\\"\", \"from\": 2319, \"to\": 2349, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2319, \"end\": 2326, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goodbye_(Gordon_Jenkins_song)\", \"score\": 0.473738066022646, \"rank\": 0.42347214710661396, \"text\": \"Goodbye\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goodbye_(Gordon_Jenkins_song)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goodbye_(Gordon_Jenkins_song)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Members of the Indian sporting fraternity have come out in support of Phogat, expressing their dismay at the CAS verdict.\", \"from\": 2351, \"to\": 2472, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2366, \"end\": 2372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"score\": 0.9996030726203521, \"rank\": 0.0003970849583531144, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\"}, {\"begin\": 2421, \"end\": 2427, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid